  "body": "When using the OpmitisticTransactionDB RocksDB can return Status.Busy when committing changes to the database (likely caused by multiple tx trying to write to the same key).\n\nThe worldstate download pipeline currently halts when we get a busy exception.\n\nWe need to catch and handle this type of exception to prevent the sync halts due to a temporary write conflict to the db.\n",
